The paper discusses the analysis of software traces, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The use of entropy measures for classification and comparison of traces involves techniques from programming languages (cs.PL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and cryptography (cs.CR). Additionally, the study involves statistical analysis and machine learning, which are areas of interest in machine learning (cs.LG).
